{"tid":1529110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求家長睇po，漏左野","createTime":"2019-09-01T16:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T04:58:54.000Z","uid":12487,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"eace7a27d178c2d2dda3ffd299ceeb5dd206b7d1","tid":1529110,"uid":12487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26de5e4193cb1319d67051d236ea49c4f0231251","tid":1529110,"uid":12487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推"},{"pid":"08aff93af5fd4d65947879466e2cb48979add612","tid":1529110,"uid":12487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d909f5e73b62aff5c36981400e7b8196d8bde7ca","tid":1529110,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/01/223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F01%2F223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif&h=16fdca9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民學唱<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國歌</span><br />\n<br />\n<em>&quot;Star Spangled Banner&quot;</em><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家仲記唔記得手足揮美國國旗唱美國國歌唱到Trump Trump都retweet!!!!</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=e91e964f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果十月一我地再幫支共賀一賀佢，搞到全美國都知支共國慶我地用美國國歌慶祝，你話會激到維尼幾咁高興？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實就無話要等到十月一既，<br />\n黎緊每次發夢都可以唱！！！！<br />\n<br />\n但大佬大家真係要練一練佢<br />\n事關首歌音域廣、歌詞繞口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MV with Lyrics: </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=f185fa72\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">Oh, say can you see by the dawn's early light</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">What so proudly we hailed at the twilight's last gleaming?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars through the perilous fight,</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">O'er the ramparts we watched were so gallantly streaming?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare, the bombs bursting in air,</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Gave proof through the night that our flag was still there.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh, say does that star-spangled banner yet wave</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?</span><br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1sKkdk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1sKkdk.gif&h=5c4ce310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, <br />\nthe Revolution of Our Times"},{"pid":"7b7175381d15f440b519d527036209063c4844cf","tid":1529110,"uid":31694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577c6aa066185f7a92756faa53d263c81737bb72","tid":1529110,"uid":12487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bb4806d14ca03bca78e06f8cbb739dce7d553e","tid":1529110,"uid":31694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19fe183f2ea5ae6030b0107a480a849ee011f8e1","tid":1529110,"uid":12487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:15:55.000Z